snippet.title: HoN 4.0: The Rise Of Apex
snippet.description:
The Final Corruption has been unleashed. HoN 4.0: The Rise of Apex hits Newerth on Dec. 13th.

For more in depth lore, check out the comic: HoN Origins: The Rise of Apex: http://lore.heroesofnewerth.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ApexComic.pdf

Play Heroes of Newerth for FREE: http://www.heroesofnewerth.com/
